  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to determine the effect of meta-cognitive therapy for insomnia.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      This study is a randomized controlled trial with 50 patients with a psychiatric disorder and
      insomnia. The patients will be randomized into two groups of 25 patients. The first group
      receives meta-cognitive therapy, whereas the second group will be assigned to a waiting list
      control.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
